column1:
Delhi High Court refuses to quash the criminal defamation case filed against Arvind Kejriwal for re-tweeting a controversial video by Dhruv Rathee.

Vikas Sankrityayan (
@MODIfiedVikas
) who filed the plea said "Dhruv Rathee posted a video wherein a number of false & defamatory allegations were made on BJP."

